creation_timestamp.description: Creation timestamp in RFC3339 text format.

description.description: An optional description of this resource.

instance.description: The Compute instance VM handling traffic for this target instance. Accepts the instance self-link, relative path (e.g. 'projects/project/zones/zone/instances/instance') or name. If name is given, the zone will default to the given zone or the provider-default zone and the project will default to the provider-level project.

name.description: Name of the resource. Provided by the client when the resource is created. The name must be 1-63 characters long, and comply with RFC1035. Specifically, the name must be 1-63 characters long and match the regular expression '[a-z]([-a-z0-9]*[a-z0-9])?' which means the first character must be a lowercase letter, and all following characters must be a dash, lowercase letter, or digit, except the last character, which cannot be a dash.

nat_policy.description: NAT option controlling how IPs are NAT'ed to the instance. Currently only NO_NAT (default value) is supported. Default value: "NO_NAT" Possible values: ["NO_NAT"]

zone.description: URL of the zone where the target instance resides.
